<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-92-0313 </DOCNO><TEXT>The paper reports the complete set of Italian normatives contained in&quot;Progetto di norma CTI -2/218&quot; which serves as a guide in the planningof gasification plants in Italy. The normatives provide definitions ofrelevant terminology and delineate specifications for components, fuels,quality control, certification and gasification plant equipment for theend-use of the gas produced.</TEXT></DOC>